sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User
    participant Browser
    participant Header as Header component
    participant Clerk as Clerk hosted UI
    participant MW as clerkMiddleware<br/>(src/proxy.ts)
    participant API as /api/searches route
    participant Auth as auth() from<br/>@clerk/nextjs/server
    participant Neon as Neon PostgreSQL

    User ->> Header: Clicks "Sign in"
    Header ->> Browser: Navigate to Clerk sign-in URL
    Browser ->> Clerk: GET Clerk-hosted sign-in page
    activate Clerk

    User ->> Clerk: Enters credentials / completes SSO
    Clerk -->> Browser: 302 to app domain<br/>+ Set-Cookie: __session=...
    deactivate Clerk

    Note over Browser: Session cookie now attached<br/>to requests for app domain

    User ->> Browser: Views SearchHistory drawer
    Browser ->> MW: GET /api/searches<br/>Cookie: __session=...
    activate MW

    MW ->> MW: clerkMiddleware resolves session,<br/>populates request auth context
    MW ->> API: forward request (pathname starts with /api/,<br/>so i18n middleware is skipped)
    activate API

    API ->> Auth: await auth()
    activate Auth
    Auth -->> API: { userId, sessionId, ... }
    deactivate Auth

    alt userId is present (authenticated)
        API ->> Neon: SELECT ... FROM searches<br/>WHERE user_id = ${userId}<br/>ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 20
        activate Neon
        Neon -->> API: Search[]
        deactivate Neon
        API -->> Browser: 200 Search[]

    else userId is null (unauthenticated)
        Note over API: No DB round trip
        API -->> Browser: 401 { "error": "Unauthorized" }
    end
    deactivate API
    deactivate MW

    Note over Browser,Header: useSearchHistory logs the 401<br/>and leaves history = []
